Note: no relegation due to league expansion.
Democrata-GV did not play the 1990 league neither in the first nor any other division,
therefore it is possible that they had been relegated but struggled in the sports courts
to secure a spot in the top flight. Eventually, they returned to the first level in 1991,
after another league expansion.

